Title: Get Their Bark Before They Bite
Description:
$p, you are a skilled herbalist, are you not? I have alchemists nearly begging at my door... well, if I had a door... for more Writhebark. We have nearly sold out! 

Will you help me gather more? I fear if the alchemists cannot create the phials they need, they will begin experimenting with my belongings.
ObjectivesText: Gather 8 Writhebark for Agrikus in Valdrakken.
